'''James Floyd''' is a freelance writer, and author of ''[[Star Wars Crossword Puzzles: And Other Word Games from a Galaxy Far, Far Away. . . .]]''.<ref name="Crossword Puzzles" /> He has written for ''[[Star Wars Insider]]'' since [[2018]]<ref name="SWI182">{{InsiderCite|182|Begun, the Clone War has!}}</ref> and the official ''[[Star Wars]]'' [[StarWars.com|website]] since 2012.<ref name="dotcombio">{{SW|url=news/contributor/jfloyd|text=James Floyd}}</ref>

He also co-contributed to the backstory of [[Melee/Legends|Melee]] appearing in the [[Databank (original)|Databank]], and also provided the first name of [[Barrow Oicunn/Legends|Barrow Oicunn]], through the ''[[What's The Story?]]'' feature of [[Hyperspace: The Official Star Wars Fan Club]].

His alias is {{U|Jawajames}} on [[Wookieepedia]].

